The main objectives of the project were to:

Build a structured Medallion Architecture for the sports company’s sales data.
Ingest raw source data into a Bronze layer.
Clean, validate, standardise, and enrich data in the Silver layer.
Create business-ready dimension and fact tables in the Gold layer.
Implement a star-schema data model for reporting and analytics.
Improve data quality, reliability, traceability, and maintainability.
Prepare the data for consumption by reporting tools such as Power BI.
